he recruiting program at VMI is designed to allow maximum flexibility for employers  You may choose from the following options or set up a schedule that is tailor made to your specific employment and scheduling requirements  general information sessions in advance classroom presentations meetings with faculty pre select resume service interview slots of specific duration pre screening testing application distribution and collection pre employment testing TO SCHEDULE  On Post interviews  presentations  resume drops  and more   go to KeydetConnect and complete the required information  New User   will click  Register Now  to register  Once registered  employer will have access to KeydetConnect at VMI  Current KeydetConnect Client   will simply enter username and password and click  GO  to access KeydetConnect at VMI  VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 